00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:34,000
a test to gauge how well it knows a certain 
set of subject material or how good it is  

233
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:40,000
at responding to a certain set of questions. 
So in the same way you take a calculus class  

234
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:43,920
and then you have calculus tests that see if 
